{"tid":1420990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組請全力谷8.5三罷既成績 罷工罷市罷課既人都唔係condom！","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:38:07.000Z","uid":41411,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ca080841b41b7286010ada4675e33e9702f575","tid":1420990,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"琴日8.5本身既主題係罷工聲援被捕人士 同時係一個意識形態既反撲<br />\n就算香港人有幾鍾意返工 係大是大非前不論公務員定其他打工仔/老細<br />\n我地都會願意企出黎！<br />\n琴日人數其實唔少　起碼係香港都未出現過咁大規模既罷工行動<br />\n７區＋機場遍地開花<br />\n雖然最後比衝擊行動搶左focus, 但都過左去 無謂再拘泥係對與錯既問題<br />\n<br />\n所以文宣組同鍵戰組 麻煩發揮你地最大既功率<br />\n我希望見到周街都講緊8月5號罷工係成功聚集到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地香港人無當義士們係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba5bf3eeacbe541d2ecf3350ac38ba758d077ea","tid":1420990,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa96a4968b28f3fad2b78f88f31d9175a59de4c4","tid":1420990,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ba3738cc605d64d8edec3194ce2e81bae23d0ee","tid":1420990,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606fc23a0ddcc0a4b3836f11f9ff4746f1f79e69","tid":1420990,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\